::Aerotaur::
     Aerotaur clutches his head firmly.  The pain from his last 
battle still confusing his senses he stumbles out of the woods into a 
clearing.  His vision finally clears and he looks around, he can just 
see the Maximal base in the distance.  He shakes his head trying to 
reorient himself and opens a com to the base.  "Maximal base, this is 
Aerotaur, could someone drag me inside... please...?"
